 Tourist in buff

 Berlin, May 23 (Reuters): A naked US tourist raised eyebrows when he went for a walk through a German city and told police he thought this was acceptable behaviour in Germany.

 We have been having unusually hot weather here lately but... we cant have this, a police spokesman in the southern city of Nuremberg said yesterday. Nude sunbathing is allowed in German public parks. 

 Oprah book 

 Chicago (AP): TV hostess

 Oprah Winfrey said she was stunned to learn her father plans to write a book about her. I was upset. I wont say devastated, but I was stunned, Winfrey told New Yorks Daily News in

 a story published on Tuesday. She said she

 laughed when an assistant told her the newspaper

 was calling to ask about a book her father

 Vernon was writing. The worst part of it was him saying: I meant to tell you Ive been working on it. 




